<p>Select a rule and enter values. Only one rule is allowed per promotion.</p>
</div>
<div class="ulist">
<ul>
<li>
<p><strong>Minimum spend</strong> = Volume discount for a minimum order value encourages buyers to buy multiple items and thus increases the order value.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>Minimum order quantity</strong> = Discounts for a minimum quantity increase the order value per shopping cart.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>Buy one get one</strong></p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>No minimum purchase</strong></p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>Volume pricing</strong> = The more items a buyer purchases, the larger the discount. Volume pricing encourages buyers to buy more than one item.</p>
<div class="olist arabic">
