</li>
<li>
<p>In the second field, enter a <strong>quantity</strong> of <strong>2</strong> and a <strong>percentage</strong> between <strong>5</strong>-<strong>79</strong>%.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>In the third field, enter a <strong>quantity</strong> of <strong>3</strong> and a <strong>percentage</strong> between <strong>6</strong>-<strong>80</strong>%.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>In the fourth field, enter a <strong>quantity</strong> of <strong>4</strong> and a <strong>percentage</strong> higher than the value entered in the third field.</p>
</li>
</ul>
