<div class="sect2">
<h3 id="_importing_promotions">1.1. Importing promotions</h3>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>You can only import promotions for which the listings were selected by creating rules. Note that promotions for which listings were selected individually can currently not be imported.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="sect2">
<h3 id="_starting_the_promotion">1.2. Starting the promotion</h3>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Once the promotion was created and saved, it has the status <strong>Draft</strong>. Click on <strong>Start</strong> to start the promotion. Depending on the start date, the promotion switches to the status <strong>Scheduled</strong> or <strong>Active</strong>.</p>
</div>
<div class="admonitionblock important">
<table>
<tbody><tr>
<td class="icon">
<i class="fa icon-important" title="Important"></i>
</td>
<td class="content">
Promotions can only be edited and changed if they have the status <strong>Draft</strong> or <strong>Scheduled</strong>. No changes can be made once a promotion has the status <strong>Paused</strong>, <strong>Active</strong>, or <strong>Ended</strong>.
</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Promotions can have the following status:</p>
</div>
<div class="ulist">
<ul>
<li>
<p><strong>Draft:</strong> Promotion can be edited, started or deleted.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>Scheduled:</strong> Promotion can be edited, paused or deleted.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>Active:</strong> Promotion can be paused or deleted.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>Paused:</strong> Promotion can be resumed or deleted.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>Ended:</strong> Promotion can be deleted.</p>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>It is not possible to restart a promotion that has already ended.
As soon as a promotion is deleted in plentymarkets it will also be deleted on eBay.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div><div class="sect1">
<h2 id="_creating_ebay_campaigns">2. Creating eBay Campaigns</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Running campaigns is a great way to attract more customers.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Find out more about eBay campaigns in the following video tutorial:</p>
</div>
<div class="videoblock">
<div class="title">eBay campaigns</div>
<div class="content">
<iframe src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/247274424" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen=""></iframe>
</div>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Use the menu <strong>Listings » eBay Campaigns</strong> to create and edit campaigns.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph instruction">
<p>Creating a campaign:</p>
</div>
<div class="olist arabic">
