<p>Go to <strong>Listings » eBay Campaigns</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click on <strong>Create new campaign</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Carry out the settings as described in <a href="#ebay-marketing-campaign-create">Table 2</a>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>Save</strong> the settings.<br>
→ The campaign will be saved and automatically started based on the start date.</p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
